BOK.F.summary: Boozt AB (publ), together with its subsidiaries, sells fashion, apparel, and beauty products online. It operates through three segments: Boozt.com, Booztlet.com, and Other. The company operates Boozt.com, a multi-brand Webstore with approximately 600 brand partners for women, men, kids, sports and athleisure, beauty, and home products. The Booztlet.com operates as a channel for inventory clearance and retailing items that were not sold during their allotted timeframe in the Webstores. It also provides clothing, shoes, accessories, sportswear, beauty products, and soft home products. In addition, the company operates two physical retail stores under the Beauty by Boozt stores name. The company operates in Sweden, Denmark, Norway, Finland, Germany, the United Kingdom, France, the Netherlands, Poland, and other European countries. Boozt AB (publ) was founded in 2007 and is headquartered in MalmÃ¶, Sweden.

RIZZO-B.ST.summary: Rizzo Group AB (publ) offers travel accessories, bags, and shoes and accessories. As of December 1, 2020, it operated through a network of 101 stores under the Accent, Morris, Rizzo, and NK names in Sweden and Norway. The company was formerly known as Venue Retail Group AB and changed its name to Rizzo Group AB (publ) in December 2020. Rizzo Group AB (publ) is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.

RNBS.ST.summary: RNB Retail and Brands AB (publ) owns, develops, and operates fashion wear, ready-to-wear clothing, accessories, jewelry, and cosmetics stores in Sweden, Norway, Finland, and internationally. It sells its products through Brothers store concept, which offers tailored and casual fashion wear for men; and Polarn O. Pyret store concept that provides clothing for babies and children. The company also sells its products through departments and stores under the NK name in Stockholm and Gothenburg; and Man of a Kind, an e-commerce concept that provides luxury brands with Nordic aesthetics, as well as offers services, such as made-to-measure, style advice, and articles for masculine style and fashion. It operates 197 stores and e-commerce platforms. RNB Retail and Brands AB (publ) is based in Stockholm, Sweden.

VRG-B.ST.short_name: Venue Retail Group AB ser. B
VRG-B.ST.summary: Venue Retail Group AB offers travel accessories, bags, and shoes and accessories. It operates through a network of 127 stores under the Accent, Morris, Rizzo, and NK names in Sweden and Norway. The company was formerly known as Wedins Shoes & Accessories AB and changed its name to Venue Retail Group AB in February 2009. Venue Retail Group AB is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.

WESC.ST.summary: WeSC AB (publ) develops and sells streetwear clothes and accessories for men and women in Sweden and internationally. Its products include hoodies, tanks, T-shirts, shirts, jackets, pants, denim, joggers, shorts, swim suits, and underwear, as well as bags, hats and slides, socks, gift cards, and mystery boxes. The company sells products under the WeSC brand name, as well as through stores and web sales. WeSC AB (publ) was founded in 1999 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
